Evocation [Cold]
Level: Sor/Wiz 2
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Medium (100 ft + 10ft/level
Effect: 10' Radius Burst
Duration: Instantaneous
Saving Throw: Reflex Half
Spell Resistance: Yes
A flurry of magic snowballs erupts from a point you select.  The swarm deals 2d6 points of cold damage to creatures and objects within the burst.  For every two levels beyond 3rd, the snowballs deal an extra die of damage, to a maximum of 5d6 at 9th level and above.